    <div class="wrapper">
      <h1>Redefining relationships between people, places and property</h1>

      <p>
       Mortar is a data and intelligence framework. Our products and platforms improve the efficiency and accessibility of services, driving digital transformation.  </p>

      <a class="cta light" href="#use-cases">Learn about our work</a>
